Eh{wait_fr:30} ehe{wait_fr:30} ehehe{wait_fr:30} eh{wait_fr:30} eehe...{waitkey}{ret}

Demon Teacher: Hey you!{nl}
You four-eyes!{nl}
Don't go breaking on your own!{waitkey}{clearbox}The one who breaks you last{nl}
is Lady Michiko!{waitkey}{clearbox}Break before that, and I'll{nl}
