Nanjo: It seems - or rather,{nl}
as I suspected - Michiko is{nl}
pulling the strings.{waitkey}{clearbox}Still, in a sense it's a{nl}
thoroughly calculated, truly{nl}
effective torture.{waitkey}{clearbox}It targets each one's weak{nl}
point, and there's no waste{nl}
in the method.{waitkey}{clearbox}And as for whether the torture{nl}
itself has any meaning -{nl}
it seems it does not.{waitkey}{clearbox}Torture for torture's sake.{nl}
Truly terrifying...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh!!{nl}
Those two! Their eyes have{nl}
already gone hollow!{waitkey}{clearbox}If we don't do something{nl}
soon, it'll become{nl}
irreversible!{waitkey}{ret}

Kuroori: A-ahahaha{nl}
Huh???{nl}
It's a fairy!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ufufufu{nl}
I really saw it!{nl}
Moootherrr!! Heheheh{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: Ohgeh!!{nl}
Keh{wait_fr:30} eh{wait_fr:30} ehh!{waitkey}{clearbox}H-huh?{nl}
A-A-Ayase!{nl}
Everyone!!{waitkey}{clearbox}H-h-h-help me!{nl}
Heeelp meee!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hmm...{nl}
Given who these guys are...{nl}
I mean...{waitkey}{clearbox}feels like a pass??{waitkey}{clearbox}But still, why's that Michiko{nl}
woman doing this?{waitkey}{clearbox}Is there even a point?{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: Ohohohoho!{nl}
It's because{nl}
they are ugly!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ugliness alone is a sin!{nl}
