Michiko, am now passing{nl}
judgment on the sin{waitkey}named "ugliness"!{waitkey}{clearbox}Do you understand,{nl}
little puppies?{nl}
Ohohohohoho!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ............{wait_fr:30}{nl}
You{wait_fr:30}... are one to talk?{waitkey}{clearbox}Never mind.{nl}
Ugly as they are, sorry to{nl}
say, they're our schoolmates.{waitkey}{clearbox}I cannot... let them die.{waitkey}{clearbox}Now, hand over{nl}
the chain key.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Y-y-y-you{nl}
Y-O-U don't get to{nl}
say that!!{waitkey}You ugly hag!!{waitkey}{clearbox}I won't forgive you!{nl}
An ugly mug like you bullying{nl}
Toro and the Demon Kid!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hurry up and unlock the{nl}
chain, stop the torture!{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: My! What thoughtful{nl}
friends you are!{waitkey}{clearbox}Beautiful friendship?{nl}
Ohohohohoho!{nl}
Lovely! Splendid!!{waitkey}Ha!! Friendship!!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Very well, in honor of that{nl}
fair friendship... I'll tell{nl}
you where the chain key{waitkey}binding these ugly men is!{waitkey}{clearbox}The chain key is on the top{nl}
floor... yes! Held by none{nl}
other than me!!{waitkey}Ohohoho!{waitkey}{clearbox}If you want to save these{nl}
ugly men, hurry to me!{nl}
Ohohoho!{waitkey}{clearbox}Yes... go straight left and{nl}
my room is right there...{nl}
Ohohohoho!{waitkey}{clearbox}But you see{waitkey}{clearbox}the "Mirror Shard" you want{nl}
so badly your hands itch{nl}
for it...{waitkey}{clearbox}lies "beyond the door behind"{nl}
where I now stand...{waitkey}{clearbox}The "Mirror Shard" is stowed{nl}
in a big chest together with{nl}
"a hint to defeat me."{waitkey}{clearbox}Ohohohohoho! This tower has{nl}
no time limit, you see,{waitkey}so fetch it at your leisure!{waitkey}{clearbox}Your friends can just endure{nl}
it a little while... hm?{nl}
Ohohohohoho!{waitkey}{clearbox}What you do is up to you!{nl}
Now then, good day!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ohohoho!{nl}
Ohohohohoho!!{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: Please help me!{nl}
The key! The key, quick!{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Geburgh!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Th-the keyyyy{waitkey}{ret}

Kuroori: Bbt{wait_fr:30} b{nl}
Bshuuu{waitkey}{clearbox}Wh-where's{nl}
th-the key{nl}
to my heart?{waitkey}{clearbox}Ze{wait_fr:30} ze{waitkey}{ret}

Demon Teacher: Come on,{nl}
come on!{nl}
Do it properly!{nl}
Hyahyahyahyahya!{waitkey}{clearbox}Drink it!{nl}
Do it!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: We can't leave them,{nl}
but the "Mirror Shard"{nl}
matters too. What do we do?{waitkey}{clearbox}Us, that is?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: More than the "Mirror{nl}
Shard," more than saving{nl}
these two, I want to go{waitkey}pummel Michiko right now...!!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: They're annoying guys,{nl}
but not bad guys.{nl}
I wanna save 'em quick!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: What a truly{nl}
unpleasant person!{nl}
That Michiko...!{waitkey}{ret}

Demon Teacher: I'm only doing{nl}
